    <section>
        <h2>Common Questions</h2>
        <h4>How do I deposit currency?</h4>
        <p>Go to the Wallet page, click on the <strong>Deposit</strong> button, and fill out the form to add a currency to your wallet.</p>

        <h4>How do I withdraw funds?</h4>
        <p>On the Wallet page, click on the <strong>Withdraw</strong> button. Select the currency and amount to withdraw. Make sure not to exceed your available balance!</p>

        <h4>How do I exchange currency?</h4>
        <p>On the Wallet page, use the <strong>Exchange</strong> button next to the desired currency. Select the target currency and amount to complete the transaction.</p>
    </section>

